    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>finely into rounds</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
