    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>pineapple</strong>,<strong> </strong>reserving the<strong> pineapple juice</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>pineapple juice</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>and<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy)</p><p>Add the juice of half your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>pineapple</strong> <strong>glaze</strong></p><p>Add<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>pineapple rings </strong>for per person (save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>to the pineapple glaze</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
