      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>glazed pineapple rings </strong>(reserving the glaze) to the pan and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until lightly charred</p><p>Once lightly charred, add your<strong> cashew nuts </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until lightly toasted – this is your <strong>charred pineapple & cashew nuts</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1662461906184-x200.jpg",
