        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once lightly toasted, transfer the <strong>charred pineapple & cashew nuts</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>greens beans</strong> in half</p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining pineapple</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1662461913991-x200.jpg",
