            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cooled coconut rice</strong>, the<strong> reserved</strong> <strong>pineapple</strong> <strong>glaze </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until the rice is warmed through – this is your <strong>fried rice</strong></p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime[s]</strong> into wedges</p>",
