    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>charred pineapple</strong> on top of the <strong>fried rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chopped spring onion</strong>, <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>toasted cashew nuts</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
